{
  "chapter": 10,
  "chapter_summary": "老伯发现律香川之妻林秀是利用鸽子向十二飞鹏帮传递机密的内奸，其叔林中鹤欠下巨额赌债被飞鹏帮金鹏坛主收买。老伯派冯浩追捕林秀，林秀的马被预先下毒致死，冯浩截获林秀后企图施暴未遂，随后揭露林秀注定要做替罪羊被杀。老伯与陆漫天驱车赶往大方客栈营救律香川，途中追忆往昔与言老大、周大胡子等人的惊险往事。律香川在大方客栈乔装苦等韩棠与方刚出现，局势一触即发。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们夫人呢？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_tou",
      "speaker_name": "丫头",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "马……马房。",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_ya_tou",
      "text": "律香川的老婆来过没有？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_tou",
      "speaker_name": "丫头",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "律夫人刚才选了匹快马，从边门出去了。",
      "tone": "怯懦",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "冯浩！",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "在。",
      "tone": "应声",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "追！带她回来！",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "陆漫天",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "你认为她才是真正的奸细？",
      "tone": "探询",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "text": "用鸽子来传递机密，比用鸽子来下酒好。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "陆漫天",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "律香川是否知情？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "text": "他若也参与其事，就不会让林秀泄露口风了，狡狯贪心的女人，并不一定聪明。",
      "tone": "沉思",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "陆漫天",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "这么样说来，我们倒冤枉了他。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "text": "我从不知道他竟如此信任女人。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "陆漫天",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "幸好他还能对付方铁鹏。",
      "tone": "安慰",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "text": "不幸的是除了方铁鹏外，必定还有很多人在大方客栈等他，万鹏王也许早已安排好了香饵，等着我送律香川去上钩。",
      "tone": "忧虑",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "陆漫天",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "我赶去，我们不能让他死。",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "text": "这一次我自己去。",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "陆漫天",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "你自己去？你怎么能亲身涉险？",
      "tone": "惊愕",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "text": "每个人都能，我为什么不能？",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "陆漫天",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "但万鹏王布下这圈套，要对付的人也许并不是律香川，而是你。",
      "tone": "警告",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "text": "那么就让他们来对付我，我正想要他们看看，孙玉伯是不是好对付的！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "看来我运气不错，想不到竟会在这里遇见你！",
      "tone": "故作镇定",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "你运气并不好。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "我的确不该选上这匹马的。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "但那时马房中只有这匹马是配好马鞍的，是不是？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "你骑来的也是匹快马。",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "只有快马才能追得上快马。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "你是特地来追我的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "老伯要你回去。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "我本来很快就会回去的，这两天我心里很闷，所以想骑马出来兜兜风，你知道我一向都很喜欢骑马。",
      "tone": "掩饰",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "我们怎么回去呢？两个人坐一匹马？",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "看来只有如此。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "我以前倒常跟香川骑一匹马，但却没有跟别人骑过，你难道不怕香川知道会不高兴？",
      "tone": "挑逗",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "你……你怎么敢对我如此无礼？",
      "tone": "惊怒",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "我只是不想再做戏了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "做戏？做什么戏？",
      "tone": "故作不解",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "你知道我是为什么来的，我也知道你想到哪里去。",
      "tone": "揭穿",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "那么你为什么不让我去？香川一向对你不错，我只不过想去告诉他，要他莫要做傻事！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "老伯要他去做的事，绝不会是傻事！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "可是……这次却不同，韩棠明明已死了，老伯为什么还要他去杀韩棠？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "我只知道遵守老伯的命令，从不问为什么，这次老伯给我的命令，是要我带你回去！",
      "tone": "坚决",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "但你可以回去说，没有追上我。",
      "tone": "哀求",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "我为什么要这样说？",
      "tone": "冷漠",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "因为……因为我一定会报答你。",
      "tone": "卑微",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "你要怎么报答我？",
      "tone": "淫邪",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "你，只要你让我去见香川一面，我什么都可以答应你。",
      "tone": "决绝",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "我若答应了你，你让我走？",
      "tone": "咬牙",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "你什么时候要？",
      "tone": "忍辱",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "现在。",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "这里好不好？我保证你以前绝没有尝过这种滋味。",
      "tone": "淫猥",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "我不是狗。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "慢慢你就会懂得，做狗有时比做人有趣得多。",
      "tone": "淫猥",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "你最好快一点，我还急着要赶路。",
      "tone": "隐忍",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "我宁可回去，带我回去见老伯。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "回去？你以为自己还能回去？",
      "tone": "狞笑",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "老伯岂非要你来带我回去？",
      "tone": "惊愕",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "老实告诉你，你早已注定哪里都不能去了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "你……你是要杀我？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "你早已注定非死不可。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "绝望",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "因为你已注定要做替罪的羔羊。",
      "tone": "残忍",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "林秀",
      "listener": "char_feng_hao",
      "text": "那你为什么还要我答应你？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_hao",
      "speaker_name": "冯浩",
      "listener": "char_lin_xiu",
      "text": "因为我是男人，遇到这种机会，谁都不会错过的。",
      "tone": "无耻",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "text": "你在想什么？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "text": "我知道你在想什么。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "陆漫天",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "text": "你是不是又想起了我们以前那段很不好过的日子？",
      "tone": "追忆",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "text": "你还记得那次我们到辰州去对付言老大的时候。",
      "tone": "追忆",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "text": "那段日子虽不好过，但现在想起来却很有趣。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "陆漫天",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "你还记不记得我们到汉阳去对付周大胡子的那次。",
      "tone": "追忆",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "text": "我当然记得，因为自从那次之后，我就决定绝不再犯同样的错误。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "陆漫天",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "这次呢？",
      "tone": "忧虑",
      "chapter": 10
    }
  ],
